	<h1 id="mods">Modifiers</h1>
        <p>
          Situational modifiers may apply, usually through reasonable
          estimates of the situation at hand.  Remember that addition
          rules for conflict resolution from the generic section of
          the rules may apply.
        </p>
        <p>
          <em>Load</em>: Divide the load in pounds by 10 and and
          subtract strength.  If this exceeds zero, subtract this from
          any physical or combat skill.
        </p>
